sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    actor Moderator
    participant ReviewerAssignmentController
    participant IReviewerAssignmentService
    participant ReviewerAssignmentService

    Note over Admin, ReviewerAssignmentController: Assign Reviewer Flow
    Admin->>ReviewerAssignmentController: POST /api/reviewer-assignments (AssignReviewerDTO)
    ReviewerAssignmentController->>IReviewerAssignmentService: AssignReviewerAsync(dto, UserId)
    IReviewerAssignmentService->>ReviewerAssignmentService: AssignReviewerAsync(dto, UserId)
    ReviewerAssignmentService-->>IReviewerAssignmentService: Assignment Result
    IReviewerAssignmentService-->>ReviewerAssignmentController: Assignment Result
    ReviewerAssignmentController-->>Admin: API Response

    Note over Admin, ReviewerAssignmentController: Auto Assign Reviewers Flow
    Admin->>ReviewerAssignmentController: POST /api/reviewer-assignments/auto-assign (AutoAssignReviewerDTO)
    ReviewerAssignmentController->>IReviewerAssignmentService: AutoAssignReviewersAsync(dto, UserId)
    IReviewerAssignmentService->>ReviewerAssignmentService: AutoAssignReviewersAsync(dto, UserId)
    ReviewerAssignmentService-->>IReviewerAssignmentService: Auto Assignment Result
    IReviewerAssignmentService-->>ReviewerAssignmentController: Auto Assignment Result
    ReviewerAssignmentController-->>Admin: API Response